The Shady Trader
[trigger settlement]
[tier 1]

*DEBUG ENCOUNTER* This encounter exists solely to help testers skip past early-game progression. It gives you a full gear loadout instantly so you can test mid- or late-game content without grinding through the starting area.

Choose a loadout below. Each option gives you 500 gold, a weapon, armor, boots, and field gear appropriate for that archetype. The third option gives top-tier equipment for testing high-difficulty content.

This encounter does not appear in production builds.

choices:

* Outdoorsman loadout = Knife, lamellar, trail boots, waterskin, guidebook, spyglass
  +give_gold 500
  +add_item hunting_knife
  +add_item lamellar
  +add_item trail_boots
  +add_item waterskin
  +add_item peoples_borderlands
  +add_item ornate_spyglass

* Combat loadout = Scimitar, brigandine, trail boots, waterskin, guidebook, spyglass
  +give_gold 500
  +add_item scimitar
  +add_item brigandine
  +add_item trail_boots
  +add_item waterskin
  +add_item peoples_borderlands
  +add_item ornate_spyglass

* Max loadout (high-difficulty testing) = Best-in-slot weapon/armor/boots + full pack upgrade + all field items
  +give_gold 500
  +upgrade_pack 4
  +add_item revathi_labrys
  +add_item mountain_regiment_armor
  +add_item windstriders
  +add_item waterskin
  +add_item peoples_borderlands
  +add_item ornate_spyglass
  +add_item ivory_comb
  +add_item lucky_buckle
  +add_item knotwork_seed
  +add_item tarnished_key
  +add_item hunters_journal
  +add_item grid_cipher
  +add_item color_lens
  +add_item revathi_tile

* Skip = Take nothing
